			<h1 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h1>

							<div class="nav-previous"><a href="https://perlancar.wordpress.com/2016/12/23/getopt-modules-23-getoptcomplete/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Getopt modules 23: Getopt::Complete</a></div>			
