				<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
					<a href="https://perlancar.wordpress.com/2016/12/24/getopt-modules-epilogue/#comment-144"><time pubdate datetime="2016-12-26T09:19:27+00:00">
					26 December 2016 at 9:19 am					</time></a>
